    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Close-fitting short coats having a short skirt, flaps, or tails, including military coats and similar items of women's fashion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
